data.title: bishopdavis
data.text:
Bishop Gregory M. Davis is one of the most sought after Bishop’s in this country. For over 30 years, Bishop Davis has been spreading the good news of the gospel of Jesus Christ and pouring out the “oil of joy in the world”. He is a founding father of the Full Gospel Baptist Church Fellowship International, where he sits on the Bishop’s Council under the leadership of his spiritual father & Founder of FGBCF, Bishop Paul S. Morton and now under the leadership of Presiding Bishop Joseph W. Walker,III.

​

He is the host Of The Greg Davis Show, a daily Radio Show heard on 910am Superstation @ 5am in Detroit, Michigan and across the State.

​

Bishop Davis is the President and CEO of Groundbreaking Productions and Entertainment and uses all aspects of media to break new ground for the Kingdom of God. Bishop Davis has penned over 14 self published books, he leads a monthly two hour healing show “Let the Healing Begin” and is also the host of Greg Davis LIVE, at 1pm daily on The Word Network, The largest African American Christian Network which reaches over 90 million homes and 200 Countries daily.
